name: petulant-bear
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.2.0" %}

package:
    name: petulant-bear
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    git_url: https://github.com/ioos/petulant-bear.git
    git_tag: v{{ version }}

build:
    number: 0
    script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt


requirements:
    build:
        - python
        - setuptools
    run:
        - python
        - netcdf4
        - numpy
        - lxml

test:
    imports:
        - petulantbear

about:
    home: https://github.com/ioos/petulant-bear
    license: GPLv3
    summary: Presents etree interface to netcdf4-python objects using NCML data model

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - benjwadams
        - daf
        - kwilcox
        - lukecampbell
        - ocefpaf
